<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <%- include('./partials/header') %>
        <title>
            <%= title %>
        </title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/docs.css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('./partials/nav', { searchQuery: '' }) %>

        <div class="docs-wrapper">
            <!-- Left Sidebar (Navigation) -->
            <aside class="docs-sidebar-left">
                <div class="docs-nav-group">
                    <div class="docs-nav-title">Company</div>
                    <a href="/about" class="docs-nav-link">About Lumina</a>
                    <a href="/mission" class="docs-nav-link">Our Mission</a>
                </div>
                <div class="docs-nav-group">
                    <div class="docs-nav-title">Legal</div>
                    <a href="/privacy" class="docs-nav-link active">Privacy Policy</a>
                    <a href="/terms" class="docs-nav-link">Terms of Service</a>
                </div>
                <div class="docs-nav-group">
                    <div class="docs-nav-title">Support</div>
                    <a href="mailto:support@lumina.com" class="docs-nav-link">Contact Us</a>
                </div>
            </aside>

            <!-- Main Content -->
            <main class="docs-main">
                <div class="docs-header">
                    <h1 class="docs-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
                    <div class="docs-meta">Last Updated: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric' ,
                            month: 'long' , day: 'numeric' }) %>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="docs-content">
                    <p>
                        At Lumina, we believe privacy is a fundamental human right. This policy outlines how we handle
                        your data with the care and respect it deserves.
                    </p>

                    <h2 id="collection">1. Information We Collect</h2>
                    <p>We believe in data minimization. We only collect what is strictly necessary to provide our
                        service:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Account Basics:</strong> Your name and email address for authentication.</li>
                        <li><strong>Profile Data:</strong> An optional bio and profile picture to represent you.</li>
                        <li><strong>Content:</strong> The stories, blogs, and comments you choose to publish.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2 id="usage">2. How We Use Your Data</h2>
                    <p>We use your information solely to:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Deliver the Lumina experience (hosting your blog, notifying followers).</li>
                        <li>Improve platform performance and security.</li>
                        <li>Send important account updates (we don't spam).</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2 id="security">3. Security</h2>
                    <p>
                        We protect your data with encryption in transit (HTTPS) and at rest. We salt and hash passwords
                        using industry-standard algorithms (bcrypt-like methods) and employ strict rate limiting to
                        prevent unauthorized access.
                    </p>

                    <h2 id="sharing">4. Data Sharing</h2>
                    <p>
                        <strong>We do not sell your data.</strong> Ever. We only share data with essential
                        infrastructure providers (like our database host) under strict confidentiality agreements.
                    </p>

                    <h2 id="contact">5. Contact Us</h2>
                    <p>
                        Questions about your privacy? Email our Data Protection Officer directly at privacy@lumina.com.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </main>

            <!-- Right Sidebar (Table of Contents) -->
            <aside class="docs-sidebar-right">
                <div class="toc-title">On this page</div>
                <nav class="toc-nav">
                    <a href="#collection" class="toc-link">Information Collection</a>
                    <a href="#usage" class="toc-link">Data Usage</a>
                    <a href="#security" class="toc-link">Security Measures</a>
                    <a href="#sharing" class="toc-link">Data Sharing</a>
                    <a href="#contact" class="toc-link">Contact Us</a>
                </nav>
            </aside>
        </div>

        <%- include('./partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>